12
00:02:47.375 --> 00:02:48.626
I don't want you to fall

13
00:02:48.710 --> 00:02:52.088
and hurt yourself again. okay?

14
00:02:53.381 --> 00:02:55.258
Do we have to go to school today?

15
00:02:55.341 --> 00:02:57.510
