55
00:05:22.780 --> 00:05:23.906
You promise?

56
00:05:23.990 --> 00:05:25.450
I promise.

57
00:05:26.951 --> 00:05:28.911
Come on. let's go. Can't be late.

58
00:05:29.454 --> 00:05:31.080
